Steps to run HCF Soak Test scenario (create,list and delete - org, space, quota and domain)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1) Update environment details in environment_details_hcftests.json:
	Location: ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/rally_properties/environment_details_hcftests.json
	
2) Update the test inputs in Json file:
   	Location:  ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/rally_properties/hcf/json_input_files/create_delete_org.json
                   ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/rally_properties/hcf/json_input_files/create_delete_quota.json
		   ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/rally_properties/hcf/json_input_files/create_delete_space.json
                   ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/rally_properties/hcf/json_input_files/create_delete_domain.json
         
3) HCF soak tests and utils details as follows:
   	Location: ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/scenarios/hcf/test_org_soak.py
		  ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/scenarios/hcf/test_quota_soak.py
                  ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/scenarios/hcf/test_space_soak.py
                  ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/scenarios/hcf/test_domain_soak.py
                  ~/cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/scenarios/hcf/utils.py

4) Context file for create and delete org:
	Location: cnap-qa/soak_perf_scale/rally_tests/scenarios/hcf/orgs.py


4) Create Deployment using the environment details file (environment_details_hcftests.json)
         Command: rally deployment create --filename="environment_details_hcftests.json" --name="hcftests"

5) Execute tests from the path where json files reside:
         Command: rally task start create_list_delete_org.json

6) check the soak test results from results
